Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.04,0:01:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)\a6}製作 ？ 秋月暮葉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.21,0:01:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 警部 你的處分下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.99,0:01:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很走運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.48,0:01:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ihla Azul 神秘與大自然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.55,0:01:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.82,0:01:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放棄！ 這也是試煉 Atsuko君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.56,0:01:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是"叢林女皇"!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泥沼中的金魚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a4}四月28日 Ihla Azul派出所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.40,0:02:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Atsuko君 你還坐在這里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.21,0:02:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早晨不是該去遺跡打掃衛生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.37,0:02:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 懈怠可是致命的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.61,0:02:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a3}Temanaga遺跡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.47,0:02:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是下雨...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.66,0:03:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 Atsuko
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里的那些家伙都在期待著呢 禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.21,0:03:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能罷手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是作為長輩的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃不掉的 你這個小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.87,0:03:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總有個名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.12,0:03:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說的話就把你交給警察
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進監獄去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.41,0:03:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 是警察嗎 有個小賊...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.51,0:03:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小鬼 別跑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不離開她身邊的話 我會變成廢物的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.53,0:04:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到小偷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.92,0:04:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 一個小賊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓她不會再犯 把她丟到河里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.11,0:04:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把腳拿開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是犯罪者 這個像毛蟲一樣的小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.02,0:04:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老娘要把你們一起送下地獄！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.43,0:04:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然叫來警察 太卑鄙了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著 我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.97,0:04:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.34,0:05:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.84,0:05:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vanessa Lee
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.26,0:05:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不餓！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a4\fad(150,50)}四月29日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.42,0:05:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的Marmalada（葡語：果醬）不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.15,0:05:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.91,0:05:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Marmalada捕獲大計劃"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對于我的“叢林女皇”來說沒有不可能的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:05:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是交易
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.94,0:06:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給阿姨這個 所以阿姨昨天請我吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也不是沒錢 只是沒有去用而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把我當成是要飯的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.76,0:06:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來你在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Marmalada捕獲大計劃"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.52,0:06:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑的寵物猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.69,0:06:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦 這種程度死不了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的錯...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.89,0:07:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要給你開個歡迎會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.89,0:07:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓你盡熟悉應這里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marmalada的事情就忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.69,0:07:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vanessa Lee是個怎樣的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.46,0:07:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vanessa嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.57,0:07:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你見過Temanaga遺跡的石頭浮雕嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在入口處有石頭浮雕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在椅子上的就是Temanaga王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.58,0:07:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女子們在向Temanaga王獻上壺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.38,0:07:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃閃發光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.06,0:07:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是"黃金之壺"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那里被稱為"沉睡的遺跡"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:08:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿著水道進入深處 是"Temanaga的房間"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說"黃金之壺"在那里 但是沒有人進去過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.06,0:08:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自古以來作為圣域受到崇拜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有時會有些破壞規矩的外來者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子的父親也是其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被帶來這里的時候還只是個15歲的小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性格逆反 總是和大家吵架 是個沒有辦法的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在則是在椰子園打工 獨自生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的父親怎么樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的父親去年死在河里了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}四月30日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 阿姨 你也太冷淡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.73,0:08:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子的那件事 是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.40,0:09:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我沒有理由道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.07,0:09:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的秘密地點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.07,0:09:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實風景會還要好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.02,0:09:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果天晴的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.24,0:09:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說了 阿姨是非常有名的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把警察和Monstro都耍得團團轉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級無敵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉出好大一塊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 你的情緒太低沉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是壞人的話 就明目張膽地去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vanessa
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.37,0:10:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么纏著我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想在這里終了一生 你的表情是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以幫你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為條件 如果你能夠幫我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Temanaga之壺"你知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.93,0:10:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那個給拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:10:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣域中的發現
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨會變得非常有名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？ 你想出名？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我想要的只是錢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.09,0:11:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為如果被發現的話 我就找不到工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等 像阿姨這樣的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(50,250)}五月1日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路不好走 請注意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里就是水道的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.51,0:11:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為圣域 禁止入內
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看這個石頭浮雕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是Temanaga王的黃金之壺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據浮雕 據說Temanaga王的房間就在水道的深處
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.69,0:11:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真相如何無人知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問那個黃金之壺是被放在什么地方展示了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個還沒有被發現
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般看法 現在還不好說Temanaga的傳說是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨 今晚動手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.87,0:12:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vanessa 遺跡里沒有什么壺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.19,0:12:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是這么說的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺跡的深處是個死胡同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:13:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是遺跡的石頭和內部擋住去路的石頭完全不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 前面還有路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父親是這樣說的 我也這樣認為
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"因為找不到 所以沒有"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是因為沒能找到 所以沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.23,0:13:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入圣域 偷走壺的話 就沒有回頭路了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里不是我該回的地方 而且我想到前方去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方？ 哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.08,0:13:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他所在的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.54,0:13:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.92,0:13:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人 有什么問題？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑著一只吉它就出發旅行的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.28,0:13:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什么要成為職業音樂人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.32,0:13:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什么呀 這個家伙是傻瓜嗎 我以前這樣想過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他已經走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話 那個家伙的歌真的不一般
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.31,0:13:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和現在的我一樣爛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種家伙的下場很簡單 很容易想象的出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我必須去找他 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:14:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 坦率 意義不明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就別浪費時間了 快點去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愿意的話 你可以不來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.04,0:14:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定今晚下手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會笑的 笑到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rock Morena？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么呢？ Ricardo
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被降職了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自告奮勇來監視你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我最了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定會與Michiko Malandro接觸的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此即使借助Monstro的力量你也不會在意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迄今為止你就是這樣做的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.17,0:14:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這么做的報償是什么？ 升職？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:14:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.61,0:14:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出賣我多少次你才滿意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.36,0:15:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來我不可能回應你的期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我和那時死撐的我不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺跡的警衛和叢林的巡邏嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.73,0:15:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一次都沒有笑過 我一直在觀察你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為這樣就能煽動我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.59,0:15:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 Ricardo
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那件事我也被Monstro盯上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoshi Batista就是這樣的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的想法根本不可能實現
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開這里的話 我就必須拼命地去找Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情 我已經受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在等我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.57,0:17:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vanessa
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里充滿了瓦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vanessa
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.02,0:17:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還能走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想死在這里嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我只能到這一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然可悲 非常不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是老是害怕這些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后還能保護自己心愛的男人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.11,0:17:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能讓你再走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了 你要是想礙事的話 就給我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什么 臭婊子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法前進了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.31,0:19:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a4}五月2日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.65,0:19:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.83,0:19:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.00,0:19:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.77,0:19:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去 就這樣去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.36,0:19:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個家伙在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在生氣嗎？ 吶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.21,0:19:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你想要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.54,0:19:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你看 Atsuko
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.09,0:20:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 這里是Ihla Azul派出所
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.82,0:20:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.54,0:20:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Atuko君嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.72,0:20:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她今天也在認真工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.18,0:20:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 那么我掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 今天早晨還沒看到她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發了 Ricardo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,0:21:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說 我會幫你升職的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.45,0:21:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.31,0:21:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標是番茄之鎮
